o. Yes -- the Duck feathers are like Fish skin, scales. Shiny, colored, irridescent. {circled:\"1\"} and I see her in a pink flannel nightgown because she is still a child -- just recently born. {circled:\"1\"} And so the Fish sign disinhibited her. This Bird/fish female deity may not be known to us. She is a UTI life form possessing fabulous technology; inserting Thomas into my brain was a medical {circled:\"84\"} procedure. There are doctors. Scientist-doctors. + our world is an ocean to them, our atmosphere like water, so she'd be a kind of aquatic bird which dives under the water - i.e. down from their world into ours. So I see her the way she sees herself. Yes -- they transferred Thomas to me, using me as a womb; he is/was one of his -- Christ's -- progeny. Christ, the Fish God Nommo. They are outside of time. This is why I saw acts + wrote about it. Thomas was transferred from there to here (then to now). He did not become awake until 2-74 jolted his memory. Before that it was as if I was picking up his dreams. So it wasn't reincarnation or even phylogenic memory; it was a scientific-medical \"embryo\" transfer, probably upon Thomas's death (which fits some of my early speculation). One of the disciples (one of the twelve) certainly would be \"her progeny.\" The Paraclete came to them at Pentecost (as narrated in Acts), so the twelve passed over into the jurisdiction of the second comforter. So one of the twelve was transferred here, to our place + time, +, in 3-74, was born again -- in an apotheosis, to actively participate in events -- in history -- in this world. + then he passed on into the next world, which is why I had the postmortem experiences. But first he had business to transact here, which he did -- very effectively. This was a medical surgical technological procedure done by a very high order of life form here + unsuspected (except it was known to the early Xtians). Thomas did not get transferred to my brain, to grow there, by any natural process.