  "evidence_excerpts": [
    {
      "text": "\"a womb for her to grow her progeny in.\" So my vision of the implanting laboratory needle was correct, with my brain as womb. And of course she's female -- only females directly have progeny. This is how you define female.\n\nThis is a life form! (i.e. Valis, who was present at the moment of birth 3-74, the apotheosis!) She took an apostolic xtian's psyche and transferred it into me (as its new womb) for it to grow through gestation to full birth as a deity. And if an apostolic xtian is her progen",
      "matched_alias": "August",
      "term_id": "TERM_august",
      "term_name": "August",
      "term_slug": "august"
    },
    {
      "text": "\"a womb for her to grow her progeny in.\" So my vision of the implanting laboratory needle was correct, with my brain as womb. And of course she's female -- only females directly have progeny. This is how you define female.\n\nThis is a life form! (i.e. Valis, who was present at the moment of birth 3-74, the apotheosis!) She took an apostolic xtian's psyche and transferred it into me (as its new womb) for it to grow through gestation to full birth as a deity. And if an apostolic xtian is her progen",
      "matched_alias": "Mary",
      "term_id": "TERM_mary",
      "term_name": "Mary",
      "term_slug": "mary"
    },
    {
      "text": "+ our world is an ocean to them, our atmosphere like water, so she'd be a kind of aquatic bird which dives under the water - i.e. down from their world into ours. So I see her the way she sees herself. Yes -- they transferred Thomas to me, using me as a womb; he is/was one of his -- Christ's -- progeny. Christ, the Fish God Nommo. They are outside of time.\n\nThis is why I saw acts + wrote about it. Thomas was transferred from there to here (then to now). He did not become awake until 2-74 jolted ",
      "matched_alias": "Pentecost",
